Text Entry Tutorial
This tutorial teaches you how to operate the keyboard when using VoiceView. The screen contains a text entry box and a keyboard. To type a letter, drag your finger around the keyboard until you hear the letter you want to type and then lift your finger.~~Try it now. When you are done, drag your finger until you locate the Next button below the text entry box. Double-tap anywhere on the screen to go to the next step in the tutorial.
